### [Comparing LLM Platforms for Defense Intelligence](/compare/llm-platforms-defense-intelligence/)
Frontier APIs vs defense-native platforms vs domain-specific RAG for intelligence analysis.

### [RAG vs Fine-Tuning for Defense NLP](/compare/rag-vs-fine-tuning/)
When to use retrieval-augmented generation versus model fine-tuning for intelligence applications.

### [Commercial Cloud vs Sovereign Deployment](/compare/commercial-vs-sovereign/)
Data residency, classification handling, and operational sovereignty trade-offs.
